<mvc:View controllerName="symposiumapp.Application.Dashboard.MyArticles.controller.MyArticles" 
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
	xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" 
	xmlns="sap.m">
	<Page enableScrolling="true" showHeader="false">
		<content>
			<Table id="idProductsTable" inset="false" items="{
			path:'/myarticles'
		}">
				<headerToolbar>
					<Toolbar>
						<content>
							<Title text="My Articles" level="H2"/>
							<ToolbarSpacer />
						</content>
					</Toolbar>
				</headerToolbar>
				<infoToolbar>
					<Toolbar active="ture">
						<Label text="your installed articles appear here"/>
					</Toolbar>
				</infoToolbar>
				<columns>
					<Column
				>
						<Text text="Article Name" />
					</Column>
					<Column	>
						<Text text="Article Subject"/>
					</Column>
					<Column	>
						<Text text="Article Type"/>
					</Column>
					<Column >
						<Text text="Presentation Type" />
					</Column>
					<Column >
						<Text text="File" />
					</Column>
					<Column >
						<Text text="Author's" />
					</Column>
						<Column >
					</Column>
				</columns>
				<items>
					<ColumnListItem>
						<cells>
							<Text text="{brdcastname}" />

							<Text text="{brdsubject}"/>
							<Text text="{abstxt}" />
							<Text text="{btypetxt}"/>
							<HBox>
								<core:Icon src="sap-icon://doc-attachment" class="size1 sapUiTinyMarginEnd" color="#031E48">
								</core:Icon>
								<Link text="{bcfname}" href="/symposiumapp{bcfpath}" class="sapUiTinyMarginEnd" />
							</HBox>
							<Button type="Transparent" icon="sap-icon://show" tooltip="Click here to see the authors of this article" press="showauthors"/>
								<Button type="Transparent" id="delbrod" icon="sap-icon://delete" tooltip="Click here to delete this article" press="deluserauthors"/>
								
								<!-- delbroadcast -->
					
						</cells>
					</ColumnListItem>
				</items>
			</Table>
			<HBox alignItems="End" justifyContent="End">
				<Button type="Transparent" id="artcancel" visible="false" icon="sap-icon://sys-cancel" tooltip="Edit File Name Ä°n System" press="closevisible"/>
			</HBox>
			<List headerText="Author's" id="artaut" visible="false" items="{path: '/artauthors'}">
				<CustomListItem>
					<HBox>
						<core:Icon size="2rem" src="sap-icon://customer" class="sapUiSmallMarginBegin sapUiSmallMarginTopBottom" />
						<VBox class="sapUiSmallMarginBegin sapUiSmallMarginTopBottom">
							<Label text="{usname}  {uslname}"/>
						</VBox>
					</HBox>
					<HBox alignItems="End" justifyContent="End">
						<Button id="delautid" type="Transparent" icon="sap-icon://delete" tooltip="remove this author" press="removeauthor"/>
					</HBox>
				</CustomListItem>
			</List>
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>